    pred:known-issue "FIXED (PR #21): production/minified builds rendered a black graph (WebGL renderer threw every frame) while hit-testing still worked. Root cause: Threlte <T.BufferAttribute> resolves its THREE class by function name; minification mangled the name so the geometry received the class instead of an instance. Guarded by a minified-build deploy gate (PR #24, tests/e2e/graph-render.test.ts + playwright.smoke.config.ts), because the bug never reproduces under `vite dev`." .

