kb:local-offload
    pred:description "Offload A: schema-constrained Ollama structured extraction (src/lib/integrations/llm/ollama-extract.ts) with a compact small-model prompt. Offload B: prefer-local routing (src/lib/integrations/llm/prefer-local.ts) — when settings.preferLocal is on and Ollama is reachable, chat/diff-summary/merge-analysis default to the ollama backend, probed via GET /api/tags with a short timeout and cache. MCP-side mirror: kb_local_extract, kb_local_summarize (opt-in via OLLAMA_BASE_URL, proposal-only)." ;
